OL,3,CFormer Consumer Energy Solutions
OL,4,Cemployees launch legal action
OL,6,FHundreds of former employees of
OL,7,FConsumer Energy Solutions (CES) are
OL,8,Ftaking legal action against an energy
OL,9,Fcompany based in Swansea after nearly
OL,10,F300 workers were made redundant.
OL,12,FThe company's closure has not only
OL,13,Fleft families facing financial
OL,14,Funcertainty, but has also prompted
OL,15,Fcalls for an investigation into its
OL,16,Foperations and its use of public money
OL,17,Fthrough a UK Government energy
OL,18,Fefficiency grant scheme.
