OL,3,CFormer Consumer Energy Solutions
OL,4,Cemployees launch legal action
OL,6,FJack Cromwell is among those affected.
OL,7,FHe joined CES in September as a site
OL,8,Fmanager coordinator, but he was one of
OL,9,Fmany made redundant in January 2026.
OL,11,F"It's upsetting, very disheartening
OL,12,Fthe way things have panned out," he
OL,13,Ftold S4C's current affairs programme Y
OL,14,FByd ar Bedwar, standing outside the
OL,15,Fcompany's now-empty offices.
OL,17,F"When I arrived at the company,
OL,18,Feverything was all guns blazing. There
OL,19,Fwas so much work going through the
OL,20,Fsystem. Targets were always going up.
