OL,6,F"Then all of a sudden we were told the
OL,7,Fcompany's future isn't certain.
OL,8,FShortly after that, we were
OL,9,Fpotentially looking at redundancy."
OL,11,F'The wool has been pulled over our
OL,12,Feyes'
OL,14,FConsumer Energy Solutions operated
OL,15,Funder the UK Government's ECO4 scheme,
OL,16,Fwhich funds free energy efficiency
OL,17,Fupgrades for homes. However, with the
OL,18,Fgrant scheme due to end in 2026, the
OL,19,Fcompany said it was no longer viable
OL,20,Fto continue trading.
