OL,6,FIn December, it launched a 45-day
OL,7,Fconsultation period to discuss the
OL,8,Ffuture of the business. But just 28
OL,9,Fdays later, on 9 January CES went into
OL,10,Fadministration.
OL,12,F"A lot of dreams were broken. There
OL,13,Fwere a lot of tears shed that day," Mr
OL,14,FCromwell said.
OL,16,F"Devastation across the board for
OL,17,Feverybody. It's had a massive impact
OL,18,Fon me. I've got bills to pay, rent to
OL,19,Fpay, council tax.
