OL,3,CFormer Consumer Energy Solutions
OL,4,Cemployees launch legal action
OL,6,F"Unless I find alternative employment
OL,7,Fsoon, I don't know how I'm going to
OL,8,Fsupport that in the long run."
OL,10,FMr Cromwell is now one of 220 former
OL,11,Femployees challenging the company's
OL,12,Fhandling of the redundancy process.
OL,13,FThe group believes the consultation
OL,14,Fperiod was not conducted lawfully.
OL,16,F"We believe they've broken the law in
OL,17,Fterms of the way the consultation
OL,18,Fperiod was conducted and them pulling
OL,19,Fout of the consultation period early,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,26,@pD@^O]xD@AOU{D@fO]
