OL,6,F"There was very minimal contact with
OL,7,Fus as well. We feel we are entitled to
OL,8,Fsome sort of compensation.
OL,10,F"A lot of us are angry because we feel
OL,11,Four concerns haven't been taken into
OL,12,Faccount by the employers. I personally
OL,13,Ffeel that the wool has been pulled
OL,14,Fover our eyes. I was sold the dream
OL,15,Fcoming here."
OL,17,FMr Cromwell has applied for more than
OL,18,F40 positions but has yet to secure a
OL,19,Fnew job.
