OL,6,F"We've been left with no job, no pay,
OL,7,Fno sort of idea on how any of us are
OL,8,Fgoing to support ourselves in the
OL,9,Ffuture. This shouldn't be happening,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FAccording to the company's most
OL,13,Frecently published financial accounts
OL,14,Fin 2024, CES reported profits of more
OL,15,Fthan #35 million.
OL,17,FThe scale of those profits has
OL,18,Fintensified scrutiny over how
OL,19,Fcompanies, such as Consumer Energy
OL,20,FSolutions, operated under the ECO4
OL,21,Fscheme.
