OL,6,FThe administrators appointed to manage
OL,7,FCES, KR8 Advisory Limited, say they
OL,8,Fare working with the Redundancy
OL,9,FPayments Service and other
OL,10,Forganisations to support affected
OL,11,Femployees.
OL,13,F"The Joint Administrators' retained
OL,14,FERA specialists have been working
OL,15,Fclosely with the Redundancy Payments
OL,16,FService (RPS) to support employees and
OL,17,Fassist with claims for other statutory
OL,18,Fentitlements, including notice pay and
OL,19,Fredundancy pay.
